label: is subject of

label: is excerpted from

label: represented by
definition: individual i is_a_nominal_measurement_of individual j' iff individual i is an instance of Nominal Measurement Information Content Entity and individual j is an instance of Entity, such that x classifies y relative to some set of shared, possibly arbitrary, characteristics.

label: is an interval measurement of
definition: individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity and y is an instance of Entity, such that x describes some attribute of y relative to a scale which has uniform intervals but has a zero value that corresponds to the absence of the attribute being measured, and additionally individual i is an instance of Interval Measurement Information Content Entity and j is an instance of Entity, such that x measures the extent or duration of y.

label: is mention of
definition: individual i is_mention_of y' iff individual i is an instance of Information Bearing Entity and y is an instance of Entity, such that individual i is used as a reference to y.

label: designated by

label: condition described by

label: language used in

definition: individual i is geospatial coordinate reference system of individual j' iff individual i is an instance of Geospatial Coordinate Reference System and individual j is an instance of Information Bearing Entity, such that individual i describes the set of standards mentioned in individual j.

label: is measured by
definition: individual i is_measured_by_ratio x' iff individual i is an instance of Entity and x is an instance of Measurement Unit, such that x describes the magnitude of measured physical quantity mentioned in individual i relative to a scale which has uniform intervals but has a zero value that does not correspond to an absence of the attribute being measured.

label: uses time zone identifier

label: uses reference system
definition: individual i uses_reference_system x of individual j' iff individual i is an instance of Information Bearing Entity and x is an instance of Reference System, such that x describes the set of standards mentioned in y, and individual j is an instance of Information Content Entity, such that y is about the characteristics by which j can be recognized or visualized.

label: uses geospatial coordinate reference system
definition: individual i uses geospatial coordinate reference system x' iff individual i is an instance of Information Bearing Entity and x is an instance of Geospatial Coordinate Reference System, such that x describes the set of standards mentioned in individual i.

label: is measured by nominal
definition: individual i X of individual j' iff individual i Y individual j [ and individual i is instance of class C and individual j is instance of class D] and additionally has the property of Z.

label: designates
definition: individual i X of individual j' iff individual i Y individual j [ and individual i is instance of class C and individual j is instance of class D] and additionally has the property of Z.

label: described by
definition: individual i .

label: is mentioned by
definition: individual i is_mentioned_by individual j' iff individual i is an instance of Entity and individual j is an instance of Information Bearing Entity, such that individual j is used as a reference to individual i.

label: prescribed by
definition: individual i X of individual j' iff individual i Y individual j [ and individual i is instance of class C and individual j is instance of class D] and additionally has the property of Z.

label: represents
definition: individual i represents y of individual j' iff individual i is an instance of Representational Information Content Entity, and y is an instance of Entity, and z is carrier of x, such that x is about y in virtue of there existing an isomorphism between characteristics of z and y.

label: prescribes
definition: individual i prescribes y of individual j' iff individual i is an instance of Directive Information Content Entity and y is an instance of Entity, such that x prescribes that some z must occur.

label: is measurement unit of
definition: individual i is_measurement_unit_of j [ and individual i is instance of Measurement Unit Information Content Entity and j is instance of Measurement Information Content Entity, such that i describes the magnitude of measured physical quantity mentioned in j.

label: is measured by ordinal
definition: individual i X of individual j' iff individual i Y individual j [ and individual i is instance of class C and individual j is instance of class D] and additionally has the property of Z.

label: is measured by interval
definition: individual i is_measured_by_interval x' iff individual i is an instance of Interval Measurement Information Content Entity and x is an instance of Measurement Information Content Entity, such that x describes some attribute of individual i relative to a scale which has uniform intervals but has a zero value that does not correspond to an absence of the attribute being measured.

label: is measured by ratio
definition: individual i Y of individual j' iff individual i is instance of Proportional Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity and individual j is instance of Entity, such that x is an instance of Information Content Entity and y is an instance of Entity, such that x describes some attribute of y relative to a scale having equal unit values and a zero value that corresponds to the absence of the attribute being measured, and furthermore, the ratio between the numerator and denominator of x is proportional to the ratio between the corresponding attributes of individual i and j.

label: is a measurement of
definition: individual i is_a_measurement_of_nominal y and individual j is an instance of Entity, such that x describes some attribute of y relative to a set of shared, possibly arbitrary, characteristics.

label: uses language
definition: individual i uses_language y' iff individual i is an instance of an Information Bearing Entity and y is an instance of a Language such that the literal value of i is a string that is encoded according to the syntax of y.

label: describes condition
definition: individual i X of individual j' iff individual i has_process_part j [ and individual i is instance of a Performance Specification and j is instance of an Event Status Nominal Information Content Entity] and additionally has the property of describes condition.

label: describes
definition: individual i is_about y' iff individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity, and y is an instance of Entity, such that individual i is about the characteristics that identify y.

label: is a ratio measurement of
definition: individual i is_a_ratio_measurement_of y" iff individual i is an instance of Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity and y is an instance of Entity, such that individual i describes some attribute of y relative to a scale having equal unit values and a zero value that corresponds to the absence of the attribute being measured.

label: is reference system of
definition: individual i is_reference_system_of individual j' iff individual i is an instance of Reference System and individual j is an instance of Information Bearing Entity, such that individual i describes the set of standards mentioned in individual j.

label: has text value
definition: individual i has text value of individual j' iff individual i has data property Y of string value Z [and individual i is instance of class C and individual j is instance of class D].

label: has datetime value
definition: individual i has datetime value' iff individual i has a data property that has as its range a datetime value.

label: has URI value
definition: individual i has URI value of individual j' iff individual i has a data property with range equal to the URI value of individual j and additionally has the property of Y [and is instance of class C or D].

label: has decimal value
definition: A data property that has as its range a decimal value.

label: has double value
definition: individual i has double value of individual j' iff individual i has a data property that has as its range a double value and individual j is instance of class C or D.

label: has date value
definition: individual i has a data property that has as its range a date value and individual j is instance of class C or D.

label: has boolean value
definition: individual i has boolean value of b at time t' iff individual i has a data property that has as its range a boolean value and the value of that property is b at time t.

label: has integer value
definition: A data property that has as its range an integer value.

label: Designative Name
definition: individual i is a Designative Name' iff individual i is a Designative Information Content Entity that consists of a string of characters that designates an entity within a specified cultural or social namespace and which is typically a word or phrase in a natural language that has an accepted cultural or social significance, and additionally, individual i is uniquely distinguishable from other entities by virtue of its designation.

label: Median Point Estimate Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Median Point Estimate Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Point Estimate Information Content Entity and additionally has a measurement that is equal to either the middle value or the average of the two values which separate the set into two equally populated upper and lower sets.

label: Civil Time Reference System
definition: individual i is a Civil Time Reference System' iff individual i is a Temporal Reference System and additionally uses_geospatial_coordinate_reference_system y, where y is an instance of Geospatial Coordinate Reference System that describes the set of standards for measuring time as well as understanding the context of and organizing temporal data.

label: Temporal Interval Identifier
definition: individual i is a Temporal Interval Identifier' iff i is a Temporal Region Identifier that designates some Temporal Interval and additionally interval equals (i, some other Temporal Interval Identifier) or interval during (some other Temporal Interval Identifier, i) or interval started by (some other Temporal Interval Identifier, i) or interval contains (i, some other Temporal Interval Identifier) or interval finishes (some other Temporal Interval Identifier, i) or interval is after (some other Temporal Interval Identifier, i) or interval is before (some other Temporal Interval Identifier, i) or interval met by (i, some other Temporal Interval Identifier) or interval started by (i, some other Temporal Interval Identifier) or interval contains (i, some other Temporal Interval Identifier) or interval starts (some other Temporal Interval Identifier, i).

label: Code Identifier
definition: individual i is a Code Identifier' iff individual i is a Non-Name Identifier that consists of a string of characters that was created and assigned according to an encoding system such that metadata can be derived from the identifier.

label: Standard Time of Day Identifier
definition: individual i is a Standard Time of Day Identifier' iff individual i is a Time of Day Identifier that designates some Time of Day using the Hours, Minutes, and Seconds of the Day that preceded the Temporal Instant.

label: Ordinal Date Identifier
definition: individual i is a Decimal Date Identifier that designates some Day by using a number to indicate the sequential ordering of the Day since the beginning of the Year.

label: Measurement Unit
definition: individual i is a Measurement Unit and additionally describes a definite magnitude of a physical quantity, defined and adopted by convention and/or by law, that is used as a standard for measurement of the same physical quantity.

label: Solar Time Reference System
definition: individual i is a Solar Time Reference System' iff individual i is a Temporal Reference System that is based on the position of the Sun in the sky and uses the time zone identifier y to describe the spatial region associated with the time zone mentioned in x.

label: Performance Specification
definition: individual i is a Performance Specification' iff individual i is a Directive Information Content Entity that prescribes some aspect of the behavior of a participant in a Process given one or more operating conditions, and additionally describes condition c, where c is an entity that is causally relevant to s existing as prescribed by p.

label: Artificial Language
definition: individual i is an Artificial Language' iff individual i is a Language that is developed through conscious planning and premeditation, rather than one that was developed through use and repetition.

label: Mode Point Estimate Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Mode Point Estimate Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Point Estimate Information Content Entity that is a measurement of a set of values and is equal to the value or values that occur most often in the set.

label: Minimum Ordinal Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity and has some attribute that is described relative to a nominally described set of like entities, where the attribute is measured by ordinal on an interval scale having no true zero value.

label: Artifact Version Ordinality
definition: individual i is a Artifact Version Ordinality' iff individual i is a An Ordinal Measurement Information Content Entity that is about the form of an Artifact which differs in some respects from previous or future forms of that Artifact.

label: Event Status Nominal Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Nominal Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of the current state of a process' iff individual i is a Y and additionally Z".

label: Information Bearing Entity
definition: individual i is a Information Bearing Entity' iff individual i is a Information Content Entity Generically Dependent Entity and additionally carries some Information Content Entity.

label: Clock Time System
definition: individual i is a Temporal Reference System' iff individual i is a Clock Time System and additionally it uses time zone identifier.

label: Spatial Reference System
definition: individual i is a Spatial Reference System' iff individual i is an instance of Information Bearing Entity and additionally describes a set of standards for uniquely identifying the position of an entity or the direction of a vector within a defined spatial region by means of measurements along one or more Coordinate System Axes.

label: Solar Calendar System
definition: individual i is a Solar Calendar System' iff individual i is a Calendar System that is designed to organize and identify dates based on the cycles of an Astronomical Body's Orbit around the Sun, where the differentia Z is described by using time zone identifier or geospatial coordinate reference system.

label: Nominal Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Nominal Measurement Information Content Entity and additionally it consists of a symbol that classifies Entities according to some shared, possibly arbitrary, characteristic.

label: Information Quality Entity
definition: individual i is a Measurement Information Content Entity and additionally it describes some Entity relative to some scale or classification scheme.

label: Priority Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Priority Measurement Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Priority Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of the relative importance of an entity.

label: Spatial Region Identifier
definition: individual i is a Spatial Region Identifier' iff individual i is a Designative Information Content Entity that designates some Spatial Region and additionally describes some characteristics of that spatial region.

label: Reference System
definition: individual i is a Reference System' iff individual i is a Descriptive Information Content Entity that describes a set of standards for organizing and understanding data of the specified type or domain, such as spatial or temporal reference systems.

label: Temporal Region Identifier
definition: individual i is a Temporal Region Identifier' iff individual i is a Designative Information Content Entity that designates some Temporal Region and additionally describes some temporal aspect of the region, such as its duration or occurrence.

label: Measurement Unit of Geocoordinate
definition: individual i is a Measurement Unit of Geocoordinate' iff individual i is a Measurement Unit specifying the geospatial coordinates of a location and additionally has latitude value and longitude value.

label: Part Number
definition: individual i is a Part Number' iff individual i is a Code Identifier that designates a type of part whose instances are designed to be part of some Artifact, and additionally it was assigned according to an encoding system such that metadata can be derived from the identifier.

label: Geospatial Coordinate Reference System
definition: individual i is a Geospatial Coordinate Reference System' iff individual i is a Spatial Reference System that is used to determine and identify the location of a point or object at or near the surface of the Earth, such that x describes the set of standards mentioned in y.

label: Natural Language
definition: individual i is a Natural Language' iff individual i is a Natural Language and additionally uses language to communicate with other individuals.

label: Date Identifier
definition: individual i is a Date Identifier' iff individual i is a Temporal Interval Identifier that designates some Day and additionally has datetime value.

label: Count Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Proportional Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity" iff individual i is a Count Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of the number of members of some aggregate and additionally uses measurement unit.

label: Temporal Instant Identifier
definition: individual i is a Temporal Region Identifier that designates some Temporal Instant' iff individual i is a Temporal Interval Identifier that designates some temporal interval and additionally the starting instant of that temporal interval is an instance of a temporal instant.

label: Julian Date Fraction
definition: individual i is a Julian Date Fraction' iff individual i is a Decimal Time of Day Identifier that designates an approximate Temporal Instant that is part of some Julian Day and has a decimal value.

label: Veracity Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Veracity Measurement Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of the extent to which a description conforms to the reality it describes.

label: Maximum Ordinal Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Maximum Ordinal Measurement Information Content Entity' iff individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity and has the greatest amount relative to a nominally described set of like entities.

label: Abbreviated Name
definition: individual i is a X' iff individual i is a Y and additionally Z, where Y is an abbreviation of a proper name and Z describes the differentia of the class.

label: Predictive Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Predictive Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Descriptive Information Content Entity that describes an uncertain future event and additionally provides information about the likelihood of the described event occurring.

label: Universal Time Reference System
definition: individual i is a Universal Time Reference System' iff individual i is an instance of Temporal Reference System and additionally uses the geospatial coordinate reference system to describe the set of standards mentioned in the label Y.

label: Non-Name Identifier
definition: individual i is a Non-Name Identifier' iff individual i is a Designative Information Content Entity that consists of a string of characters that designates an entity within a specified namespace or context, is not a Designative Name, may be automatically or randomly generated, and typically has no preexisting cultural or social significance.

label: Algorithm
definition: individual i is a Directive Information Content Entity that prescribes some Process and contains a finite sequence of unambiguous instructions in order to achieve some Objective' iff individual i is a Directive Information Content Entity that prescribes some Process and contains a finite sequence of unambiguous instructions in order to achieve some Objective, where the label of its parent class or genus is Algorithm.

label: Distance Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of a One-Dimensional Extent inhering in some Site that is externally connected to two Independent Continuants, and additionally describes the extent or quantity of the distance between the two Independent Continuants.

label: Diminutive Name
definition: individual i is a Diminutive Name' iff individual i is a Diminutive Name and additionally it designates some Proper Name.

label: Designative Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Designative Information Content Entity' iff individual i is an instance of Y and additionally Z".

label: Probability Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of the likelihood that a Process or Process Aggregate occurs.

label: Spherical Coordinate System
definition: individual i is a Spherical Coordinate System" iff individual i is an ordered triple of numerical coordinates that consist of the radial distance of the point of interest from a fixed origin, its polar angle measured from a fixed zenith direction, and the azimuth angle of its orthogonal projection measured from a fixed direction on a reference plane that passes through the origin and is orthogonal to the zenith.

label: Deviation Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Deviation Measurement Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of the extent to which an entity conforms to how it is expected or supposed to be.

label: Geospatial Region Bounding Box Identifier List
definition: individual i is a Geospatial Region Bounding Box Identifier List' iff individual i is a Measurement Unit of Geocoordinate that is comprised of 4 pairs of coordinates, one for each of the 4 defining points (North, West, South, East) of some Geospatial Region Bounding Box.

label: Point Estimate Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Point Estimate Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Point Estimate Information Content Entity that consists of a single value for the measured entity.

label: Julian Day Number
definition: individual i is a Julian Day Number' iff individual i is a Decimal Date Identifier that designates some Julian Day by using a number to indicate the sequential ordering of the Day since the Julian Date epoch.

label: Time of Day Identifier
definition: individual i is a Temporal Instant Identifier that designates some Time of Day and additionally satisfies the property 'instant is after' or 'is inside instant of' or 'interval equals' or 'last instant of' or 'interval contained by' with respect to some other Temporal Interval Identifier.

label: Time Zone Identifier
definition: individual i is a Time Zone Identifier' iff individual i is a Spatial Region Identifier that designates the region associated with some uniform standard time for legal, commercial, or social purposes and additionally has a longitude value.

label: Julian Date Identifier
definition: individual i is a Julian Date Identifier' iff individual i is an instance of a Time Zone Identifier that designates some Julian Day using a decimal value.

label: Proportional Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a measurement of a portion of a whole (described by the numerator) compared against that whole (described by the denominator) where the whole is a nominally described set of like entities, and additionally i is measured by ratio.

label: Descriptive Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Descriptive Information Content Entity' iff individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity and has properties that describe some Entity.

label: Calendar System
definition: individual i is a Calendar System' iff individual i is a Temporal Reference System that is designed to organize and identify dates, and additionally has date value.

label: Decimal Date Identifier
definition: individual i is a Decimal Date Identifier' iff individual i is a Decimal Time of Day Identifier that designates an approximate Temporal Instant that is part of some Day and is specified using a decimal value for the portion of the Day that preceded the Temporal Instant.

label: Mean Point Estimate Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Mean Point Estimate Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Point Estimate Information Content Entity that is equal to the sum of all the values in the set divided by the total number of values in the set.

label: Acronym
definition: individual i is a Non-Name Identifier' iff individual i is a Designative Information Content Entity that consists of a string of characters that does not follow an encoding system, and additionally it designates another entity within a specified context.

label: Lunar Calendar System
definition: individual i is a Lunar Calendar System' iff individual i is a Calendar System that is designed to organize and identify dates based on the cycles of the Moon's phases, and additionally has temporal part c, where c is a Calendar Date Identifier that designates some Day by using a combination of Day, Week, Month, or Year Identifiers formatted according to an implementation of a Calendar System.

label: Arbitrary Identifier
definition: individual i is a Non-Name Identifier' iff individual i is a Non-Name Identifier and additionally it consists of a string of characters that does not follow an encoding system.

label: Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Generically Dependent Continuant that generically depends on some Information Bearing Entity and stands in relation of aboutness to some Entity, and additionally consists of a set of propositions or images (as in the case of a blueprint) that prescribe some Entity.

label: Prescriptive Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity and additionally prescribes some Entity, such that x serves as a rule or guide for y if y an Occurrent, or x serves as a model for y if y is a Continuant.

label: Decimal Time of Day Identifier
definition: individual i is a Decimal Time of Day Identifier' iff individual i is a Time of Day Identifier that designates an approximate Temporal Instant that is part of some Day and is specified using a decimal value for the portion of the Day that preceded the Temporal Instant.

label: Nickname
definition: individual i is a Nickname' iff individual i is a Designative Name that is a familiar or humorous substitute for an entity's Proper Name and additionally it designates the same entity as its parent genus.

label: Ordinal Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Priority Measurement Information Content Entity' iff individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity and it describes some attribute of another Entity relative to a scale ordered by rank, such that the attribute being measured is the priority or importance of the Entity being described.

label: Proper Name
definition: individual i is a Proper Name' iff individual i is a Designative Name and additionally it designates some Entity.

label: Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Measurement Information Content Entity that consists of a symbol that places a Quality of an Entity onto an interval scale having a true zero value, and additionally, individual i is measured by ratio.

label: Sequence Position Ordinality
definition: individual i is a Sequence Position Ordinality' iff individual i is a Sequence Position Ordinality and additionally has some ordinal measurement that describes its position in some ordered sequence.

label: Representational Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Representational Information Content Entity' iff individual i is an instance of an Information Content Entity that represents some Entity.

label: Interval Estimate Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity and is equal to the Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of a set of values and is equal to the absolute difference between the largest value and the smallest value in the set.

label: Sidereal Time Reference System
definition: individual i is a Sidereal Time Reference System' iff individual i is a Temporal Interval that is equal to the approximate length of time required for an Astronomical Body to complete one rotation around its Rotational Axis as specified relative to a particular Temporal Reference System, and additionally uses a fixed Star or Stars as reference points.

label: Data Range Interval Estimate Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Data Range Interval Estimate Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Ratio Measurement Information Content Entity that is equal to the absolute difference between the largest value and the smallest value in the set, and additionally describes some attribute of an Entity relative to a scale having uniform intervals but has a zero value that does not correspond to an absence of the attribute being measured.

label: Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Measurement Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Descriptive Information Content Entity that describes the extent, dimensions, quantity, or quality of some Entity relative to some standard and additionally uses measurement unit.

label: Language
definition: individual i is a Language' iff individual i is a Directive Information Content Entity that prescribes a canonical format for communication and additionally contains a set of rules for using symbols to represent meaning.

label: Estimate Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of an entity based on partial information about that entity or an appropriately similar entity' iff individual i is a Measurement Information Content Entity that is a measurement of some Entity y relative to some scale or classification scheme, and the extent to which y conforms to how it is expected or supposed to be.

label: Priority Scale
definition: individual i is a Priority Scale' iff individual i is a Reference System that is designed to be used to rank or identify the importance of entities of the specified type, and additionally it describes a set of standards for organizing and understanding data of the specified type or domain.

label: Military Time Zone Identifier
definition: individual i is a Military Time Zone Identifier' iff individual i is a Time Zone Identifier that designates a spatial region where the local time is calculated according to the specified offset from Zulu time, which has no offset from Coordinated Universal Time, and additionally uses_time_zone_identifier y for some other Information Bearing Entity y.

label: Initialism
definition: individual i is an Initialism' iff individual i is a Designative Name that consists of the initial letters of some words (or syllables) in a Designative Name, and in which each letter is pronounced separately.

label: Reliability Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Reliability Measurement Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Reliability Measurement Information Content Entity and additionally describes the extent to which an entity can consistently produce an outcome.

label: Lot Number
definition: individual i is a Lot Number' iff individual i is a Lot Number and additionally has integer value.

label: Temporal Reference System
definition: individual i is an instance of Information Bearing Entity and x is an instance of Reference System, such that x describes the set of standards mentioned in y.

label: Legal Name
definition: individual i is a Proper Name that is an official name for the designated entity as determined by a Government or court of law' iff individual i is a Y and additionally Z, where Z is 'designates other entities within some context'.

label: Calendar Date Identifier
definition: individual i is a Calendar Date Identifier' iff individual i is a Date Identifier that designates some Day by using a combination of Day, Week, Month, or Year Identifiers formatted according to an implementation of a Calendar System.

label: Cartesian Coordinate System
definition: individual i is a Cartesian Coordinate System' iff individual i is a Spatial Reference System that identifies each point in a spatial region of n-dimensions using an ordered n-tuple of numerical coordinates that are the signed (i.

label: Greenwich Mean Time Zone Identifier
definition: individual i is a Time Zone Identifier that designates a spatial region where the local time is calculated according to the specified offset from Greenwich Mean Time' iff individual i is a Time Zone Identifier and additionally uses_time_zone_identifier y, such that y designates the spatial region associated with the time zone mentioned in x.

label: Interval Measurement Information Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Interval Measurement Information Content Entity that places a Quality of an Entity onto some interval scale having no true zero value.

label: Media Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Descriptive Information Content Entity' iff individual i is a Representational Information Content Entity and additionally consists of a set of propositions that describe some Entity.

label: Certificate
definition: A Media Content Entity that attests to certain demonstrated characteristics of an Object, Person, or Organization.

label: Academic Degree
definition: individual i is a X' iff individual i has satisfactorily completed a course of study and additionally holds a Certificate issued by an Educational Organization to indicate that completion.

label: Image
definition: individual i is a Media Content Entity' iff individual i is a Image and additionally represents some entity owing to a visual isomorphism between the carrying artifact and the entity.

label: Chart
definition: individual i is a Chart' iff individual i is a Image that is designed to carry some Representational Information Content Entity that is prescribed by some canonical visual format, and additionally has a WKT property.

label: Database
definition: individual i is a Database' iff individual i is a Descriptive Information Content Entity that is designed to be rapidly searchable and retrievable.

label: List
definition: individual i is a Sequence Position Ordinality Entity and additionally carries some Code Bearing Entities that represent some Information Content Entities.

label: Code List
definition: individual i is a Code List' iff individual i is an ordered sequence of Code Identifiers.

label: Video
definition: individual i is a Media Content Entity that contains a sequence of representations that are presented sufficiently rapidly to create the appearance of motion and continuity' iff individual i is a Video and additionally it describes some specific entity or scene in such a way that the representation of the entity or scene appears continuous to human viewers.

label: Message
definition: individual i is a Message iff individual i is a Information Content Entity that is relatively brief and designed to be transmitted from a sender to a recipient, and additionally has_sender x, where x is an instance of Agent and sends y, such that y is an instance of Act Of Communication and decoder of the InformationContentEntity intended for communication in y.

label: Warning Message
definition: individual i is a Warning Message' iff individual i is a Notification Message designed to bear an Information Content Entity that describes a possible or impending threat.

label: Email Message
definition: individual i is a Email Message' iff individual i is a Email Box and additionally has_recipient some Agent y, such that x sends i to y.

label: Notification Message
definition: individual i is a Notification Message' iff individual i is an Act Of Communication that has_sender x and has_recipient y, such that y is an instance of Agent and decoder of the InformationContentEntity intended for communication in x, and x prescribes p, and p describes_condition c, and c is an entity that is causally relevant to i existing as prescribed by x.

label: Barcode
definition: individual i is a Barcode' iff individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode or Two-Dimensional Barcode and additionally represents some Directive Information Content Entity as WKT.

label: Two-Dimensional Barcode
definition: individual i is a Two-Dimensional Barcode' iff individual i is a Two-Dimensional Barcode and additionally represents some Directive Information Content Entity in the form of WKT.

label: Aztec Code
definition: individual i is a Two-Dimensional Barcode' iff individual i is a Aztec Code and additionally it represents a transportation industry ticket that can be scanned using a barcode reader.

label: Data Matrix Code
definition: individual i is a Data Matrix Code' iff individual i is a Two-Dimensional Barcode that consists of cells arranged in rectangular patterns and is used for marking small items in logistics and operations, and additionally has double value.

label: QR Code
definition: individual i is a QR Code' iff individual i is a Two-Dimensional Barcode that consists of numeric, alphanumeric, binary, or kanji information and is used primarily for tracking and marketing.

label: PDF417 Code
definition: individual i is a PDF417 Code' iff individual i is a Two-Dimensional Barcode that is used in applications that require the storage of huge amounts of data and additionally has a WKT property with a string value.

label: One-Dimensional Barcode
definition: individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode' iff individual i is an instance of Information Bearing Artifact and represents some Directive Information Content Entity as WKT.

label: Codabar Barcode
definition: individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode' iff individual i is an instance of Codabar Barcode and additionally represents numbers 0-9 and the characters -$:/.

label: Code 93 Barcode
definition: individual i is a Code 93 Barcode' iff individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode and additionally has 93 ASCII characters that are used in logistics to identify packages in retail inventory, lable electornic components, and provide supplementary delivery information.

label: ITF Barcode
definition: individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode that consists of an even number of numerical characters and is used primarily in packaging and distribution' iff individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode that represents an even number of numerical characters and is used primarily in packaging and distribution.

label: MSI Plessey Barcode
definition: individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode' iff individual i is an instance of MSI Plessey Barcode and additionally represents an indefinite number of numerical characters and is used for inventory control and marking storage containers and shelves in warehouse environments.

label: EAN Barcode
definition: individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode that represents 8 or 13 numerical digits and is used to scan consumer goods' iff individual i is a EAN Barcode and additionally has decimal value.

label: ISSN Barcode
definition: individual i is a ISSN Barcode that designates a periodical' iff individual i is an instance of EAN Barcode and additionally represents a periodical.

label: JAN-13 Barcode
definition: individual i is a EAN Barcode' iff individual i is an instance of Information Bearing Entity and additionally has text value y, where y consists of 13 numerical digits in the format #nnn#nnn#nnn#.

label: EAN-13 Barcode
definition: individual i is a EAN-13 Barcode' iff individual i is an instance of Information Bearing Entity and additionally has as its range a string formated according to the Well-known text standardization for geometric objects.

label: EAN-8 Barcode
definition: individual i is a EAN-8 Barcode" iff individual i is a EAN-8 Barcode and additionally represents 8 numerical digits and is used to designate products at the point of sale.

label: ISBN Barcode
definition: individual i is a ISBN Barcode' iff individual i is a EAN Barcode and additionally has text value 'ISBN

label: GS1 DataBar Barcode
definition: individual i is a GS1 DataBar Barcode' iff individual i is an instance of One-Dimensional Barcode that consists of 12-14 numerical digits and is used in retail and healthcare, and additionally has text value representing 12-14 numerical digits.

label: Code 39 Barcode
definition: individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode' iff individual i is a Code 39 Barcode and additionally has 39 characters that are numbers 0-9, capital letters A-Z, or the symbols -.

label: Code 128 Barcode
definition: individual i is a Code 128 Barcode' iff individual i is a One-Dimensional Barcode and additionally represents to 128 ASCII characters and is used primarily in supply chains.

label: UPC Barcode
definition: individual i is a UPC Barcode' iff individual i is a UPC Barcode and additionally consists of 6 or 12 numerical digits and is used to scan consumer goods.

label: UPC-A Barcode
definition: individual i is a UPC-A Barcode' iff individual i is an instance of Information Content Entity and x is an instance of UPC-A Barcode, such that x represents 12 numerical digits.

label: UPC-E Barcode
definition: individual i is a UPC-E Barcode' iff individual i is a UPC-E Barcode that consists of 6 numerical digits and represents a product at the point of sale.

label: Information Line
definition: individual i is a Media Content entity consisting of a single line or row in some Document Content entity of which it is a part' iff individual i is an instance of Information Line and additionally satisfies the property that it consists of a single line or row.

label: Document Field Content
definition: individual i is a Document Field Content' iff individual i is a Document Field and additionally it prescribes the eliciation of information to be written or selected within the document content entity.

label: Document Content Entity
definition: individual i is a Document Content Entity' iff individual i is a Representational Information Content Entity that consists of a series of paragraphs of text or diagrams that are intended to be carried by physical pieces of paper or an electronic word processor file.

label: Book
definition: individual i is a Document Content Entity that canonically appears as ink on paper or parchment, or other materials fastened together to hinge at one side' iff individual i is a Book and additionally it has the property of being designed to bear some specific Information Content Entity by means of ink, paper, parchment, or other materials fastened together to hinge at one side.

label: Transcript
definition: individual i is a Document Content Entity that was originally recorded in a different medium' iff individual i is a Descriptive Information Content Entity that consists of a set of propositions that describe some Event, and additionally i is a Document Content Entity that was originally recorded in a different medium.

label: Spreadsheet
definition: individual i is a Document Content Entity that canonically appears as a interactive, tabular form' iff individual i is a Spreadsheet and additionally has Document Fields as parts in which to write or select prescribed content.

label: Report
definition: individual i is a Document Content entity that conveys an account of some event, situation, or the result of some observation or inquiry' iff individual i is a Document and additionally it conveys an account of some event, situation, or the result of some observation or inquiry.

label: Journal Article
definition: individual i is a Document Content Entity that is part of a Journal Issue' iff individual i is a Journal Article and additionally it is designed to bear some specific brief composition on a specific topic as part of a Journal Issue.

label: Twenty-Four-Hour Clock Time System
definition: individual i is a Twenty-Four-Hour Clock Time System' iff individual i is a Temporal Reference System that is a convention for keeping and displaying the Time of Day, indicated by the Hours passed since midnight, from 0 to 23.

label: Julian Calendar
definition: individual i is a Julian Calendar System' iff individual i is a Julian Year and additionally has date value.

label: Twelve-Hour Clock Time System

label: Earth-Centered Earth-Fixed Coordinate System
definition: individual i is a X' iff individual i is an independent continuant and x is an instance of Geospatial and Cartesian Coordinate System, such that x identifies positions using an x-axis, y-axis, and z-axis coordinate where the zero point is the center of the Earth, the z-Axis extends toward the North Pole but does not always coincide exactly with the Earth's Axis of Rotation, the x-Axis extends through the intersection of the Prime Meridian and the Equator, the y-Axis completes the right-handed system, and all three axes are fixed to the Earth such that they rotate along with the Earth.

label: Gregorian Calendar
definition: individual i is a Gregorian Calendar System' iff individual i is a Solar Calendar System that has a regular Year of 365 24-Hour Days divided into 12 Months with a leap day added at the end of February every 4 Years except Years that are evenly divisible by 100 but not 400 such that there are 97 leap Years every 400 Years and the average length of a Gregorian Year is 365.
